{"tid":1537061,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"明居正：老共目標係10月1日前大抓捕，打重傷不打死，但錯手殺一兩個可接受","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:39:53.000Z","uid":179666,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa6d60ef91bf6dbf1173b25296bf7b978923be3","tid":1537061,"uid":179666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:42:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sK2biNYNEjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsK2biNYNEjw&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=cb39fb93\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sK2biNYNEjw</a><br />\n<br />\n佢講得好有道理 老共想喺中秋之前 平息事件， 勇武可唔可以 起碼等到月中， 先繼續 行動？ <br />\n<br />\n因為月中之前呢段短時間內行動， 如果明居正講嘅係啱 ，對方一定滲內鬼 在前線帶風向， 設陷阱去大量捉前線手足， 我唔敢講今晚搭巴士係咪其中一個陷阱 大家盡量小心， 我覺得就當做呢兩個星期 休整一下， 月尾再同佢哋做預祝國慶準備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99455306358071b68b3afa8b2ad95b3bca96d859","tid":1537061,"uid":297850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4jkVvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4jkVvH.jpg&h=4ef20020&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e7a3ac314faca99eb9457bd2afde5e2a71be114","tid":1537061,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post